api Actions with STS.

AssumeRole:
    Allows you to assume a role to obtain temporary security credentials.
AssumeRoleWithSAML:
    Allows you to assume a role using a SAML authentication response.
AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity:
    Allows you to assume a role using a web identity federation token.
DecodeAuthorizationMessage:
    Decodes additional information about the authorization status of a request from an encoded message returned in response to an AWS request.
GetCallerIdentity:
    Returns details about the IAM identity whose credentials are used to call the API.
GetFederationToken:
    Returns a set of temporary security credentials for a federated user.
GetSessionToken:
    Returns a set of temporary security credentials for an AWS account or IAM user.